quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,87,"Illa rahmatan min rabbika innafadlahu kana AAalayka kabeera"
  17,88,"Qul la-ini ijtamaAAati al-insu waljinnuAAala an ya/too bimithli hatha alqur-ani laya/toona bimithlihi walaw kana baAAduhum libaAAdinthaheera"
  17,89,"Walaqad sarrafna linnasifee hatha alqur-ani min kulli mathalin faabaaktharu annasi illa kufoora"
  17,90,"Waqaloo lan nu/mina laka hattatafjura lana mina al-ardi yanbooAAa"
  17,91,"Aw takoona laka jannatun min nakheelinwaAAinabin fatufajjira al-anhara khilalahatafjeera"
  17,92,"Aw tusqita assamaa kamazaAAamta AAalayna kisafan aw ta/tiya billahiwalmala-ikati qabeela"
  17,93,"Aw yakoona laka baytun min zukhrufin aw tarqafee assama-i walan nu/mina liruqiyyika hattatunazzila AAalayna kitaban naqraohu qul subhanarabbee hal kuntu illa basharan rasoola"
  17,94,"Wama manaAAa annasa anyu/minoo ith jaahumu alhuda illa an qalooabaAAatha Allahu basharan rasoola"
  17,95,"Qul law kana fee al-ardi mala-ikatunyamshoona mutma-inneena lanazzalna AAalayhim mina assama-imalakan rasoola"
  17,96,"Qul kafa billahishaheedan baynee wabaynakum innahu kana biAAibadihikhabeeran baseera"
